  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UploadPolicy
    Deprecated. 
    This class is of no use, as it actually behaves exactly as the DefaultUploadPolicy.

    @Deprecated
public class CustomizedNbFilesPerRequestUploadPolicy
extends DefaultUploadPolicy
    These is a now deprecated specialization of DefaultUploadPolicy. The DefaultUploadPolicy now reads itself the nbFilesPerRequest applet parameter.
